claim: Mary Steenburgen stars in The Proposal.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Her other film appearances include Cross Creek  (  1983  )  , Parenthood  (  1989  )  , Back to the Future Part III  (  1990  )  , Philadelphia  (  1993  )  , What 's Eating Gilbert Grape  (  1993  )  , Elf  (  2003  )  , The Brave One  (  2007  )  , Step Brothers  (  2008  )  , The Proposal  (  2009  )  , and The Help  (  2011  )  .
